ents</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>INTERNSHIP </strong></span></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Completed Engineering Internship on GSM Networks and MNP Technology in Bharti Airtel Ltd. Gurgaon.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Worked as an Intern in NTPC Ltd. Faridabad acquiring knowledge about the Electricity Generation Process at the Gas Power Plan.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>EXTRA CURRICULAR ACTIVITIES AND SOCIETIES</strong></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Vice President of IEEE Club, Project Head of Literary Club, Co-Editor of College Magazine</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Vice-President | IEEE Club  2013-2014</strong></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Successfully executed the Technical fest focused on promoting the “Startup Culture”</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Held various technical seminars concentrated on Robotics, Embedded Systems, Network Design</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Co-Editor | College magazine ‘Epiphany’</strong></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Circulated 500 copies of the magazine among students and staff</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Project Head | Literary Club <span style=\"color: #333399;\">2012-2013</span></strong></span></h4>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Organized several inter-college debate and speech events</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Arranged events for the students to develop strong communication skills</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row height=\"small\" us_bg_image=\"470\" us_bg_repeat=\"no