sed','closed','','','','','2018-04-30 16:45:19','2018-04-30 16:45:19','',0,'http://www.richarajput.com/?page_id=594',0,'page','',0),(595,1,'2018-04-30 16:45:19','2018-04-30 16:45:19','','','','inherit','closed','closed','','594-revision-v1','','','2018-04-30 16:45:19','2018-04-30 16:45:19','',594,'http://www.richarajput.com/594-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(600,1,'2018-06-19 02:38:48','2018-06-19 02:38:48','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\">RICHA RAJPUT</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">GOOGLE | MICROSOFT | HUBSPOT </span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">CERTIFIED DIGITAL MARKETING SPECIALIST</span></strong></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row us_bg_image=\"470\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #999999;\">SAGE PUBLICATIONS INDIA PVT. LTD.</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Make <strong>Marketing Plans</strong> for promotion of forthcoming and new released titles and understanding key business priorities and support through focused marketing initiatives.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Electronic Campaigning</strong> - Create e-mailers for specific subject databases for promotion of various subject categories and titles.</li>\r\n 	<li>New acquisitions email campaigning and important days to focus on titles for promotion for target-specific groups.</li>\r\n 	<li>Make author mailers and New Release mailers for pre pub. Promotion of forthcoming titles.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Print Campaigning</strong> – Execute the promotional print campaigns planned and scheduled as per the annual Marketing Plan for books.</li>\r\n 	<li>Undertake the creation of <strong>marketing print collaterals</strong>  including catalogues, brochures, leaflets, advertisements, posters and flyers, collateral for books events; and announcements regarding books at various instances, required for books’ promotion and fulfillment of marketing objectives.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Brand Advertisement Management </strong>– Magazine ads, Journal Ads, Online Ads on Flipkart, Infibeam, Biblio banners</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Social Media Marketing</strong>: Facilitate promotions of library titles on different social media handles like Facebook, Twitter, Linkedin, Instagram.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Blogging </strong>– Writing Blog posts to engage targeted audience</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Make Marketing &amp; Conversion Reports:</strong> Make Conversion and Book Reports</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Proofreading:</strong> Collation, compilation, editing and proofreading of content for design of the required collateral.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Website Content Management:</strong> Make Advance Information of forthcoming titles to ensure that information about SAGE India books is regularly updated on all the company websites.</li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Responsible for reviewing the content updated on the website platform to ensure same is error free.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row height=\"small\" us_bg_image=\"470\" us_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #999999;\">RUZZELL WEARS INDIA</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Handled Brand Management operations through <strong>Digital Marketing, Social Media and Email Marketing, Corporate and E-Commerce Website Development and Maintenance, Content Writing/Editing and</strong> <strong>Business Development operations.</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">KEY RESULT AREAS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Survey marketplace for new and existing web marketing trends, competitive marketing plans/ optimization strategies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Managing online brand and product campaigns to raise brand awareness.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Involved in company corporate and e-commerce website development,  front-end design and maintenance.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Running E-Mail marketing campaigns.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Ruzzell  Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest, Youtube, Linkedin and Quora Page Management for social media promotions  in order to maximize site traffic and sales demand.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Social Media/ Digital/ Print Media Content Management through the production of website content, Blogs, Articles, Press Release, Brochure, Social media posts and Advertorials.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Editing and Proof reading editorial content like articles, Blogs, Product descriptions, social media content for errors in structure, spelling, punctuation and overall grammar ensuring zero errors.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Keeping pace with emerging online trends to increase effectiveness of Digital marketing and promotions in the Digital Space.</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Involved in Business Development operations and help company in collaborating with other brands.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row height=\"small\" us_bg_image=\"470\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #999999;\">MANAV RACHNA VIDYANTARIKSHA PVT. LTD.</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000